# Global Security Headers (The Iron Dome)

/_
Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'none'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://cdn.ampproject.org https://_.ampproject.org; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com data:; img-src 'self' data: https://www.google-analytics.com https://_.google-analytics.com https://analytics.google.com https://stats.g.doubleclick.net; connect-src 'self' https://cdn.ampproject.org https://_.ampproject.org https://www.googletagmanager.com https://www.google-analytics.com https://\*.google-analytics.com https://analytics.google.com https://ampcid.google.com https://stats.g.doubleclick.net; frame-src 'self' https://www.google.com; worker-src 'self' blob:; manifest-src 'self'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests;
Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
X-Frame-Options: DENY
Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), autoplay=(self), camera=(), display-capture=(), encrypted-media=(), fullscreen=(self), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), interest-cohort=(), keyboard-map=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), midi=(), payment=(), picture-in-picture=(self), publickey-credentials-get=(), screen-wake-lock=(), sync-xhr=(), usb=(), web-share=(self), xr-spatial-tracking=()
